{"tid":1588193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果發夢唔小心整親，記得去打破傷風針","createTime":"2019-09-22T16:55:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T17:31:05.000Z","uid":132227,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"c11784de08c3bbd12483d1a6db6ba570e969780e","tid":1588193,"uid":132227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:55:03.000Z","msg":"香港出世應該打齊破傷風針<br />\n之後一針有效10年<br />\n即係你近10年有打過都夠用<br />\n<br />\n如果最近發夢比路邊石仔/鐵枝整損<br />\n記住去打破傷風針，以防萬一<br />\n<br />\n最簡單喺急症室已經可以打 雖然等耐啲<br />\n大學生既話好多大學都會有得打<br />\n唔好怕醜怕尷尬 你唔洗同佢講喺咩場合整親<br />\n求其講踩單車或者仆親已經夠 冇人會深究<br />\n<br />\n最緊要身體健康先可以繼續發夢無後顧之憂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"1d61045ec52c01b1d04aa421d5820b5394e75fda","tid":1588193,"uid":239539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:56:26.000Z","msg":"有個新諗法<br />\n約一日出黎 928 929 又好<br />\n全港人拎住輕汽球 約埋喺維港 汽球上面印有自由民主 五大訴求等字眼 一齊放上天比外媒影住 有冇得諗？"},{"pid":"499c56effc925b39e54001d02640175cc2b74dc3","tid":1588193,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:57:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"996513e52b0967e5d1c25d39b494f520b55348dd","tid":1588193,"uid":295904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"499c56effc925b39e54001d02640175cc2b74dc3","tid":1588193,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T16:57:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:00:38.000Z","msg":"做左 警察了？"},{"pid":"090715bdbea886947a59bd942234628ded530633","tid":1588193,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T17:04:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1587564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1587564</a>"},{"pid":"6425c7aec67a31a2f1305fd89d7cdb61d9518c0e","tid":1